strings:
<voice_0x01001778><se_def>*: Master Chen Mui! What a surprise!
It has been many years. When did you return?

<voice_0x01001779><se_low>Chen Mui: Save the pleasantries!
You must tell me what is happening here!
<voice_0x0100177A><se_low>Chen Mui: ...I apologise. That's a matter for me to discuss with the Council Elders. Pray, let us pass.

<voice_0x0100177B><se_def>*: Most honoured Chen Mui.
You may pass, but I cannot permit the humans to enter the council chamber with you.

<voice_0x0100177C><se_low>Chen Mui: We are facing a dire crisis,
and you stand on formalities!?

<voice_0x0100177D><se_low>Chen Mui: I will take full responsibility for my guests.
Now move out of my way at once!
<voice_0x0100177E><se_def>*: It appears your mind is made up, Master Chen Mui. In that case, please enter.
